Class PropertyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • play.db.ebean.Model
      • models.PropertyType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.avaje.ebean.bean.EntityBean, java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class PropertyType
extends play.db.ebean.Model
    This Class is part of the defined dynamic property pattern by Martin Fowler. It must not be instanced directly but will be managed by the Project-class. PropertyTypes are saved by its Projects using the cascade mechanism.
